1. egg文件生成和使用   参考文档 : http://berdy.iteye.com/blog/1106662
1.1 安装easy-install

1.2 制作egg

(1) 新建目录egg-demo 新建文件 setup.py (setup.py其实是python工具包distutils的配置文件，setuptools就是基于 distutils来做的)
(2) 编辑 setup.py 文件如下 : 
#!/usr/bin/env python 
#-*- coding:utf-8 -*- 

from setuptools import setup 
setup() 

(3) 使用下面命令生成egg包 : 
python setup.py bdist_egg 
查看文件类型 : file dist/UNKNOWN-0.0.0-py2.6.egg
查看zip文件内部结构 : unzip -l dist/UNKNOWN-0.0.0-py2.6.egg

(4) 重新编辑setup文件 
#!/usr/bin/env python 
#-*- coding:utf-8 -*- 

from setuptools import setup, find_packages 

setup( 
name = "demo", 
version="0.1.0", 
packages = find_packages(), 
zip_safe = False, 

description = "egg test demo.", 
long_description = "egg test demo, haha.", 
author = "amoblin", 
author_email = "amoblin@ossxp.com", 

license = "GPL", 
keywords = ("test", "egg"), 
platforms = "Independant", 
url = "", 
) 

生成打包目录
$ mkdir demo 
$ cat demo/__init__.py 
#!/usr/bin/env python 
#-*- coding:utf-8 -*- 

def test(): 
print "Hello, I'm amoblin." 

if __name__ == '__main__': 
test() 

重新打包


