(6) 卸载
查看安装信息 : 
$ cd /usr/local/lib/python2.6/dist-packages 
$ cat easy-install.pth|grep demo 
./demo-0.1.0-py2.6.egg 
$ ls -F|grep demo 
demo-0.1.0-py2.6.egg/ 
卸载 : 
删除easy-install.pth中对应的行 
删除目录 demo-0.1.0-py2.6.egg

